							<div class="span6 right">
								<p>We are calling on the Prime Minister to support a new law to protect children who become victims of bullying. 
								Ayden&#39;s Law would:</p>
								<ol>
									<li>Make bullying and intimidation a criminal offence</li>
									<li>Make corporate neglect a criminal offence, leaving schools and colleges legally accountable for bullying</li>
									<li>Protect children from cyberbullying</li>
									<li>Increase community-based bullying prevention</li>
									<li>Support families with children who bully to change their behavior</li>
								</ol>
